text: Come to the Stable is a 1949 American comedy drama movie directed by Henry Koster and stars, Loretta Young, Celeste Holm, Elsa Lanchester, Hugh Marlowe, Thomas Gomez, Dorothy Patrick. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox and was nominated for 7 Academy Awards in 1950. ==References== ==Other websites== * * * Category:1949 comedy movies Category:1940s comedy-drama movies Category:1949 drama movies Category:American comedy-drama movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Henry Koster
